    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a dream and has been kept tucked away in a garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels and smells brand new, you\u2019ve found it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
