    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it is in flawless condition! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure it\u2019s always sparkling clean. There isn't a single blemish on it, and the interior still smells brand new. It runs like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You won't find another one this pristine! Come take a look and see for yourself!",
      "price": 45500.0,
