      "description": "Available now is a museum-quality BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. This specimen boasts a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanical integrity is paramount; preventative maintenance includes documented rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis is exceptionally rigid, retaining its original suspension geometry and bushings for a visceral, analog driving experience. Finished in a flawless factory coat with an immaculate interior, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering.",
